VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT resource\s+"aws_db_instance"[^}]*publicly_accessible\s*=\s*true
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:publicly_accessible\s*=\s*true && MISSING:# intentional|# development|# staging
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects RDS instances configured to be publicly accessible from the internet.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for RDS Instance Publicly Accessible.
